HEADWORD: Evilness
<hw>E"vil*ness</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The condition or quality of
being evil; badness; viciousness; malignity; vileness; <as>as,
<ex>evilness</ex> of heart; the <ex>evilness</ex> of sin.</as></def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

